data.description: YOU ALWAYS DREAMED OF COUNTRY STYLE LIVING CLOSE TO TOWN....WELCOME HOME To This All Brick Custom Built Country Home!!! Unincorporated yet close to Winfield, Troy or Wentzville w/ super low taxes Resting Peacefully on 2 Level Acres, Backing to Trees boasting Bonus 16 X 14 Out Garage/Building. Composite Decking.  Nearly 3,000 Total Living Area & includes 2 Potential Wood Burning Fireplaces, updated Luxury Vinyl Flooring throughout most of Main Floor, Newer Stainless Steel Appliances, Newer Furnace and Newer Roof in 2023 & 35 X 25  3 Car Garage Spaces. Spacious Main Floor Laundry/MudRoom w/ second Hook Ups Lower Level.  Lower level could easily be In Law Quarters with TWO SEPARATE WIDE Staircases. . Master Suite Updated Double Sink Vanity, Walk In Shower.  Unincorporated!!!  There's Much to Like about this All Brick Ranch.  ASSUMABLE VA Loan....Come By and Take a Look!!!
